<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>其实</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>只要能做到玩耍学习两不误</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><strong>既强健体魄</strong></span><strong>又不耽误成绩</strong></span></p>
